@TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5130

### Get saga state by trip ID (use trip ID from Trip.API)
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
Accept: application/json

### Get saga state - non-existent (404)
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### List all sagas (first page)
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### List sagas filtered by state
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas?state=Completed&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### List sagas filtered by customer ID
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas?customerId=c1111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### List sagas filtered by state and customer
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/api/sagas?state=AwaitingPaymentAuthorisation&customerId=c1111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111&page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Health check
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Liveness check
GET {{TripBooking.Saga.API_HostAddress}}/alive
Accept: application/json

